extends layout

block content

  if cert == 'OK'
    h1(style='margin-top: 100px;') Now you are our member! Log in and create Story now.
  else
    h1(style='margin-top: 100px;')= title
    h2 Make your own stories. Practice on that stories.

    h2 My contents  
  
    if error
      p Error getting dynamic content.
    else

      p Your library has the following record counts:

      ul.tite
        li #[strong Books: ]
          a(href='/catalog/books') !{data.book_count}
        li #[strong Stories: ]
          a(href='/catalog/stories') !{data.story_count}
        li #[strong Genres: ]
          a(href='/catalog/genres') !{data.genre_count}

      p To create your first story or book, create genre first.<br/>
      |for example, Article, Address, Fantasy.